# News Parser Agent Environment Variables

# Required: API key for z.ai or Anthropic
# Get your key from: https://console.z.ai
ZAI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here

# Alternative: Use Anthropic's API directly
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# Optional: Custom base URL (defaults to z.ai)
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.z.ai/api/anthropic

# Optional: X/Twitter Authentication (Headless Mode)
# If not set, the tool will use browser-based authentication via 'bird login'
# Headless auth is recommended for CI/CD, Docker containers, and servers
#
# To extract these tokens:
# 1. Open x.com in your browser while logged in
# 2. Open DevTools (F12) → Application → Cookies → https://x.com
# 3. Find and copy: auth_token (value column) → AUTH_TOKEN
# 4. Find and copy: ct0 (value column) → CT0
#
# Security: Treat these as sensitive credentials. Never commit to git.
# Tokens expire periodically and may need refreshing.
#
# AUTH_TOKEN=your_auth_token_value_here
# CT0=your_csrf_token_value_here
